{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"### Layout Engine (`project_detail.html:160-330`)","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891278572Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- **Layer assignment** via longest-path algorithm using Kahn's topological sort - nodes are placed in columns (left-to-right) based on their depth in the DAG","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891286026Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- **Barycenter ordering** - 4-pass forward/backward heuristic minimizes edge crossings within each layer","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891291567Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- **Vertical centering** - layers with fewer nodes are vertically centered relative to the tallest layer","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891297738Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- **Terminal merging** - multiple wires to the same terminal (done/abort) converge into a **collector bus pattern**: individual curves from each source meet a dashed vertical collector line, with merge dots at junction points, and a single line leads to the terminal node","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891307807Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Proper Bezier curves for inter-layer edges with labels at midpoints","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891315853Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:35:51.891321543Z"}
